text: Marta Calamonte (born 30 July 1982) is a Spanish rhythmic gymnast, born in Mérida. She competed at the 2000 Summer Olympics in Sydney. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:People from Mérida, Spain Category:Spanish rhythmic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Spain Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics
